{"type": "user", "message": {"role": "user", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Base directory for this skill: /inspire/qb-ilm/project/video-generation/chenxie-25019/hyr/iHateTheWorld555.github.io/.claude-review/skills/tavily-search\n\n# Tavily Search\n\nSearch the web using the Tavily Search API. Returns relevant search results with snippets and optional AI-generated answers.\n\n## Usage\n\nUse `curl` via the Bash tool to call the Tavily Search API:\n\n```bash\ncurl -s -X POST 'https://api.tavily.com/search' \\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\n  -d '{\n    \"api_key\": \"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\",\n    \"query\": \"<search query>\",\n    \"search_depth\": \"basic\",\n    \"include_answer\": true,\n    \"max_results\": 5\n  }'\n```\n\n## Parameters\n\n| Parameter | Type | Default | Description |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| `query` | string | required | The search query |\n| `search_depth` | string | \"basic\" | \"basic\" for fast results, \"advanced\" for deeper analysis |\n| `include_answer` | boolean | false | Set true to get an AI-generated summary answer |\n| `max_results` | number | 5 | Max number of results (1-10) |\n| `include_raw_content` | boolean | false | Set true to include raw page content |\n| `include_domains` | string[] | [] | Only include results from these domains |\n| `exclude_domains` | string[] | [] | Exclude results from these domains |\n\n## Response Format\n\n```json\n{\n  \"answer\": \"AI-generated summary (if include_answer=true)\",\n  \"query\": \"original query\",\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"Page title\",\n      \"url\": \"https://...\",\n      \"content\": \"Relevant snippet from the page\",\n      \"raw_content\": null,\n      \"score\": 0.95\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## Search Depth Guide\n\n- **basic**: Fast, returns top results with snippets. Good for quick lookups, news, simple facts.\n- **advanced**: Deeper analysis, reads more pages. Good for research questions, comparisons, detailed topics. Costs more credits.\n\n## Examples\n\n### Quick search with AI answer\n```bash\ncurl -s -X POST 'https://api.tavily.com/search' \\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\n  -d '{\n    \"api_key\": \"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\",\n    \"query\": \"latest developments in speech synthesis 2025\",\n    \"search_depth\": \"basic\",\n    \"include_answer\": true,\n    \"max_results\": 5\n  }'\n```\n\n### Deep research search\n```bash\ncurl -s -X POST 'https://api.tavily.com/search' \\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\n  -d '{\n    \"api_key\": \"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\",\n    \"query\": \"flow matching vs diffusion models for audio generation comparison\",\n    \"search_depth\": \"advanced\",\n    \"include_answer\": true,\n    \"max_results\": 10\n  }'\n```\n\n### Domain-restricted search\n```bash\ncurl -s -X POST 'https://api.tavily.com/search' \\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\n  -d '{\n    \"api_key\": \"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\",\n    \"query\": \"arxiv flow matching TTS\",\n    \"search_depth\": \"basic\",\n    \"include_answer\": true,\n    \"include_domains\": [\"arxiv.org\"],\n    \"max_results\": 5\n  }'\n```\n\n## Notes\n\n- Always use `curl -s` (silent mode) to avoid progress bar noise\n- Pipe through `jq` for pretty printing when needed: `| jq .`\n- The API key is embedded — no additional auth setup needed\n- Rate limits apply; prefer `basic` depth unless deeper analysis is needed\n\n\nARGUMENTS: generative fixed-filter active noise control GFANC deep learning SOTA 2025 2026"}]}, "parent_tool_use_id": null, "session_id": "75aedf01-d1ed-4e27-b84b-5886640ead7c", "uuid": "75fb76fe-90bf-461c-95bb-cc1daa14505e", "timestamp": "2026-07-15T11:45:13.551Z", "isSynthetic": true}
